title: Panda Star
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Chinese, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Chinese restaurant with a vegetarian menu section that includes many tofu and mock chicken dishes. The spring rolls and possibly the chow mein is made from egg noodles - so vegans should ask. The veggie/tofu fried rice is vegan. While the regular menu is meat-based, this is an option to get vegetarian dishes in the area. Bargain lunch specials.
